' ============================================================
' Legend
' ============================================================

legend right
  |= 色 |= 意味 |
  | <#6BCB77> | ✅ 完了 / MERGED / CLOSED |
  | <#4D96FF> | 🔵 実行中 / IN REVIEW |
  | <#FFD93D> | ⏳ 待機中 / 手動操作必要 |
